index.shtml	page for customers; fills in form processed at bibfile.php
bibfile.php	processes form, saves input as file.bib and calls bibproc.cgi
bibproc.cgi*	reference conversion program
subrebib.pl*	subroutine of bibproc.cgi	shared with ~/scripts
subxmlbib.pl*	subroutine of bibproc.cgi	shared with ~/scripts
subcrossxml.pl	subroutine of bibproc.cgi	shared with ~/scripts
cr.pl		subroutine of bibproc.cgi

breakurl.sty@	auxiliary
eptcs.bst@	auxiliary
eptcs.cls@	auxiliary
nocite.tex	auxiliary, called from bibproc.cgi
nocite.rebib	generated, called from subrebib.pl and subxmlbib.pl
file.bib	generated bibliography, created by bibfile.php and called from nocite.tex


query.cgi*	form feeding into doilookup.cgi, called from previous bibproc.cgi and from above
doilookup.cgi*	interface with crossref, called from query

Doilookup.cgi*  interface with crossref, shows output locally (not in use)

parameters from query to doilookup: workshop, paper, restype, first, last.

